Introduction

  The file notifier plugin provides a simple file based notifier.

Usage

  Example configuration:
  
+--
<notifier name="file">
	<file:file xmlns:file="urn:be:e-contract:jwatchdog:notifier:file:1.0"
		file="/home/fcorneli/jwatchdog-notifications.txt" />
</notifier>
+--

